description:
What causes hair loss? How do hormones contribute to loss of hair? Could poor digestion be part of the problem? Learn what factors contribute to hair loss and what you can do to reverse the trend. Barbara O’Neill discusses factors that contribute to hair loss and explains how to make a mixture you can apply to your scalp to nourish and stimulate hair follicles to encourage growth.
